---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="About CatBrothers" description="CatBrothers: cat science and health backed by veterinary research. Meet the author.">
  <section class="about">
    <div class="container about__inner">
      <div class="eyebrow">About</div>
      <h1>About <em class="script-accent">CatBrothers</em></h1>

      <div class="about-author">
        <h2>Vladys Z.</h2>
        <p class="author-subtitle">App Developer &middot; Professional Chef &middot; Cat Science Enthusiast</p>
      </div>

      <p>I'm Vladys — cat dad, app developer, and professional chef. CatBrothers combines two of my passions: cats and digging into the science behind why they do what they do.</p>

      <p>As a chef, I'm obsessed with cat nutrition — what's really in their food and what they actually need. As a developer, I love analyzing the research papers behind feline behavior.</p>

      <p><strong>CatBrothers</strong> exists because most cat content online is myths and clickbait. Here, every fact is backed by veterinary science and peer-reviewed studies.</p>

      <h2>Why This Blog?</h2>
      <p>I started CatBrothers after spending hours reading veterinary journals to understand my own cats' health issues. I realized this information should be accessible to every cat owner — not buried in paywalled academic papers. Every article cites real studies, names specific institutions, and gives you practical advice you can use today.</p>

      <h2>My Promise</h2>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Real science</strong> — Every claim comes with a source: veterinary studies, institutions, verified data</li>
        <li><strong>Zero products to sell</strong> — I don't promote expensive gadgets or affiliate-pushed products</li>
        <li><strong>Personal experience</strong> — I share what I've learned as a cat owner and nutrition-obsessed chef</li>
        <li><strong>Free forever</strong> — All knowledge is free and accessible</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Also on YouTube</h2>
      <p>I post daily cat science tips on <a href="https://www.youtube.com/@CATBROTHERS2" target="_blank" rel="noopener">@CATBROTHERS2</a> — quick, evidence-based content about cat health and behavior.</p>

      <h2>Contact</h2>
      <p>vladys.z96@gmail.com</p>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .about { padding: 3rem 0; }
  .about__inner { max-width: var(--content-width); }
  .about__lead {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    color: var(--color-text-light);
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }
  .about-author { margin-bottom: 2rem; }
  .author-subtitle { font-size: 1.1rem; color: var(--color-text-light); margin-top: 0.25rem; }
  .about h2 { margin-top: 2rem; margin-bottom: 0.75rem; }
  .about p { margin-bottom: 1rem; color: var(--color-text-light); line-height: 1.7; }
  .about ul { padding-left: 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
  .about li { margin-bottom: 0.5rem; color: var(--color-text-light); }
</style>
